snippet.title: Scott Buckley
snippet.description:
Cinematic Creative Commons music by Scott Buckley. Everyone has a story, and I have a library of my own cinematic original music - released under CC-BY 4.0 - to help you tell that story, in whatever format you tell it. Oh, and it's free - just as long as you credit me.

Find more music in my library over at scottbuckley.com.au/library.
